headline: Moody’s assigns Issuer ratings to Bank of Åland Plc
summary: Bank of Åland PlcStock exchange releaseOctober 7, 2025, 15.00 EEST Moody’s assigns Issuer ratings to Bank of Åland Plc The rating agency Moody’s Ratings (“Moody’s”) has today assigned Bank of Åland Plc (Ålandsbanken Abp) a long- and short-term issuer rating of Baa1/P-2. The long-term issuer rating carries a positive outlook.
